ay%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201955-1957%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201955-1957%2520-%25200650.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F8150b004ade0565d32aa4d88b21d2892#page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=To Rockaways: Beach Trains In Operation|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252023%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%25201956-1957%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%25201956-1957%2520-%25200241.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F147cd4c4e78bb11637387bbb8e8e3a06#page=1|accessdate=2016-08-16|work=Greenpoint Weekly Star|agency={{link-en|Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com}}|date=1956-06-29|page=2|archive-date=2021-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211013152443/https://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%2023%2FBrooklyn%20NY%20Greenpoint%20Daily%20Star%2FBrooklyn%20NY%20Greenpoint%20Daily%20Star%201956-1957%2FBrooklyn%20NY%20Greenpoint%20Daily%20Star%201956-1957%20-%200241.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F147cd4c4e78bb11637387bbb8e8e3a06#page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[JFK特快|JFK特快]]由曼哈頓向東提供一條往[[約翰·F·甘迺迪國際機場|約翰·F·甘迺迪國際機場]]的連結，自1978年起至1990年為止以此站為總站，並包括此站到機場內的免費接駁巴士服務。巴士服務在JFK特快列車停運後繼續營運，成為機場與霍華德海灘車站的唯一連接<ref name="NYLeader-JFKExp-Sep1978" /><ref name=NYTimes-JFKExp-2009>{{Cite web|url=http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/11/25/if-you-took-the-plane-to-the-train-sing-the-jingle/|title=If You Took the Train to the Plane, Sing the Jingle|last=Grynbaum|first=Michael M.|access-date=2016-07-03|date=2009-11-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027021816/http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/11/25/if-you-took-the-plane-to-the-train-sing-the-jingle/|archivedate=2015-10-27}}</ref><ref name="MTI-JFKAirtrain-May2012">{{cite web|url=http://transweb.sjsu.edu/PDFs/research/2503/2503_cases/2503-cs2-jfk-airtrain.pdf|title=CASE STUDY REPORT: JOHN F. KENNEDY INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT AIRTRAIN|last2=Freeman|first2=Dennis|date=May 2012|website=[[聖荷西州立大學|sjsu.edu]]|publisher={{link-en|明內塔交通學院|Mineta Transportation Institute|Mineta Transportation Institute}}, [[聖荷西州立大學|San Jose State University]]|last1=Gosling|first1=Geoffrey D.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106192733/http://transweb.sjsu.edu/PDFs/research/2503/2503_cases/2503-cs2-jfk-airtrain.pdf|archivedate=2017年1月6日|df=|access-date=2017年7月8日}}</ref><ref name="UCL-AirtrainJFK-Sep2011" />。

車站在2000年代早期大規模翻新，並進行5000萬美元的重建以將地鐵與新的[[甘迺迪國際機場捷運|甘迺迪國際機場捷運]]連接。整項計劃由{{link-en|STV集團 (美國)|STV Group (United States)|STV集團}}設計並有[[紐約與新澤西港務局|紐約與新澤西港務局]]財政支援<ref name="MTI-JFKAirtrain-May2012" /><ref name="STVInc-HowardBchJFK">{{cite web|title=AirTrain JFK Howard Beach Intermodal Center|url=http://www.stvinc.com/pdf/AirTrain%20JFK%20Howard%20Beach.pdf|publisher={{link-en|STV集團 (美國)|STV Group (United States)|STV Group (United States)}}|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820055319/http://www.stvinc.com/pdf/AirTrain%20JFK%20Howard%20Beach.pdf|archivedate=2016-08-20|access-date=2017-07-08}}</ref><ref name="RailwayGaz-AirtrainJFK-Mar2004">{{cite news|url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/airtrain-jfk-opens-for-service.html|title=AirTrain JFK opens for service|date=2004-03-01|work=[[國際鐵路公報|Railway Gazette International]]|accessdate=2016-07-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822091917/http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/airtrain-jfk-opens-for-service.html|archivedate=2016-08-22}}</ref>。車站重建期間拆除了原有地鐵月台，並新月台和夾層興建期間在中央軌道建立了臨時月台，離峰時段列車以單線軌道營運<ref name="ERA-HowardJFK-Oct2002">{{cite journal|last1=Glucksman|first1=Randy|title=Commuter and Transit Notes|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=October 2002|volume=45|issue=10|pages=13|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-10-bulletin/13|accessdate=2016-08-27|publisher=Electric Railroaders Association|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920170742/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-10-bulletin/13|archivedate=2016-09-20}}</ref><ref name="ERA-HowardJFK-Oct2002-2">{{cite journal|last1=Erlitz|first1=David|title=Track Construction Forecast For October, 2002 in the NYC Transit System|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=October 2002|volume=45|issue=10|pages=18–19|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-10-bulletin/18|accessdate=2016-08-27|publisher=Electric Railroaders Association|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920170314/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-10-bulletin/18|archivedate=2016-09-20}}</ref><ref name="ERA-HowardBch-Nov2002">{{cite journal|last1=Erlitz|first1=Jeffrey|title=Tech Talk|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=November 2002|volume=45|issue=11|pages=7, 19|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-11-bulletin/7|accessdate=2016-09-04|publisher=Electric Railroaders' Association|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920190037/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-11-bulletin/7|archivedate=2016-09-20}}</ref>。車站附近的機場捷運結構在2001年完工<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesledger.com/stories/2001/19/20010510-archive326.html|title=AirTrain construction starts on Jamaica station|last=Scheinbart|first=Betsy|date=2001-05-10|work=Times Ledger|access-date=|via=|accessdate=2016-07-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803040630/http://www.timesledger.com/stories/2001/19/20010510-archive326.html|archivedate=2016-08-03}}</ref>，而機場捷運車站在2003年12月17日完工開放，接駁巴士服務也隨之終止<ref name="MTI-JFKAirtrain-May2012" /><ref name="RailwayGaz-AirtrainJFK-Mar2004"/>。該轉乘十分受歡迎，2003年至2007年間地鐵與機場捷運的轉乘就有超過400萬人次<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/03/25/realestate/25LIVING.html|title=Prices Aren’t Supersonic; the Planes Aren’t Either|last=Hughes|first=C. J.|date=2007-03-25|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-07-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806101937/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/03/25/realestate/25LIVING.html|archivedate=2017-08-06}}</ref>。

2012年[[颶風桑迪|颶風桑迪]]對IND洛克威線造成嚴重破壞，此站一度在其南面的車站整修期間成為A線列車的南端總站。往洛克威的列車服務在2013年5月30日重新開放<ref name=asandy>{{cite web|title=Rebuilding the Rockaways After Hurricane Sandy|url=http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/RebuildingRockawaysAfterHurricanSandy.htm|work=mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|accessdate=2012-11-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121129020912/http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/RebuildingRockawaysAfterHurricanSandy.htm|archivedate=2012-11-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="MTA-ATrain-Rkwy-May302013">{{cite news|title=A Train Service Restored to Rockaways|url=http://www.mta.info/news/2013/05/30/train-service-restored-rockaways|work=[[大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|date=2013-05-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509092706/http://www.mta.info/news/2013/05/30/train-service-restored-rockaways|archivedate=2016-05-09|accessdate=2017-07-08}}</ref>。
