車站的夾層位於地鐵月台和軌道的上方，一個現代化、恆溫和以玻璃包裹的大樓<ref name="UCL-AirtrainJFK-Sep2011"/><ref name="STVInc-HowardBchJFK" />，全長90英呎<ref name="NYLeader-JFKExp-Sep1978">{{cite news|title=New "JFK Express" Service Begun in Howard Beach|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252023%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201978%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201978%2520-%25200687.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Ffbdb4829ac4f2348d1ab4d5338ab9a6c#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-22|work=New York Leader Observer|agency={{link-en|Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com}}|date=1978-09-28|archive-date=2021-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003020959/https://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252023%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201978%2FForest%2520Parkway%2520NY%2520Leader%2520Observer%25201978%2520-%25200687.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Ffbdb4829ac4f2348d1ab4d5338ab9a6c#page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兩側都設有大型不鏽鋼標誌顯示「{{lang|en|Howard Beach JFK}}」。夾層大樓設有小型票務處和三個閘機區，設於地鐵、機場捷運和未付費區之間<ref name="UCL-AirtrainJFK-Sep2011">{{cite news|title=Project Profile; USA; New York Airtrain|url=http://www.omegacentre.bartlett.ucl.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/USA_AIRTRAIN_PROFILE.pdf|accessdate=2016-07-23|work=[[倫敦大學學院|UCL]] {{link-en|巴特雷特|The Bartlett|Bartlett School of Planning}}|date=2011-09-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817073215/http://www.omegacentre.bartlett.ucl.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/USA_AIRTRAIN_PROFILE.pdf|archivedate=2016-08-17}}</ref><ref name="STVInc-HowardBchJFK" />。
