車站的機場捷運部分設有一個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和兩條軌道，位於車站複合的上層。月台的東端可前往C泊車區<ref name="ERA-AirtrainTour-Dec2002"/>。與紐約地鐵車站不同，機場捷運車站月台完全密封，並設有[[月台幕門|月台幕門]]，以助車站維持恆溫和避免乘客跌入軌道。軌道上設有感應器偵測列車的位置，並只在完全對齊時才會打開車門。如此可容許機場捷運以[[列車自動運行裝置|列車自動運行裝置]]而且無人駕駛情況下運行<ref name="RailwayGaz-AirtrainJFK-Mar2004"/><ref name="ERA-AirtrainTour-Dec2002"/>。

月台全長約240英呎<ref name="RailwayGaz-AirtrainJFK-Mar2004"/><ref name="ERA-AirtrainTour-Dec2002">{{cite journal|last1=Berger|first1=Raymond R.|title=A Tour of the JFK Airtrain|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=December 2002|volume=45|issue=12|pages=4, 16|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-12-bulletin/16|accessdate=2016-08-27|publisher=Electric Railroaders Association|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920170318/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2002-12-bulletin/16|archivedate=2016-09-20}}</ref>。東南面下一站是{{link-en|勒弗茲林蔭路車站 (機場捷運車站)|Lefferts Boulevard (AirTrain JFK station)|勒弗茲林蔭路}}<ref name="ERA-AirtrainTour-Dec2002"/>。由於此線是[[紐約與新澤西港務局|紐約與新澤西港務局]]擁有，捷運與地鐵使用不同的[[閘機|閘機]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/ind/howard_beach_jfka/index.php|title=Howard Beach-JFK Airport (A, Airtrain JFK) - The SubwayNut|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|website=www.subwaynut.com|access-date=2016-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817191534/http://subwaynut.com/ind/howard_beach_jfka/index.php|archivedate=2016-08-17}}</ref>。乘客必須在進入或離開時繳費，因為此站和{{link-en|牙買加車站 (長島鐵路)#機場捷運車站|Jamaica (LIRR station)#AirTrain station|牙買加車站}}是唯二繳費的車站。MetroCard的自動售票機設於閘機區的兩側<ref name=ERA-AirtrainJFK-Jan2004>{{cite journal|last1=Berger|first1=Raymond R.|last2=Mercado|first2=Raymond J.|title=JFK Airtrain Update - Revenue Passenger Service Begins|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=January 2004|volume=47|issue=1|pages=17–18|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2004-01-bulletin/17|accessdate=2016-08-27|publisher=Electric Railroaders Association|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920170748/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2004-01-bulletin/17|archivedate=2016-09-20}}</ref><ref name=costs>{{cite web |url=http://www.panynj.gov/airports/jfk-cost-tickets.html |title=Cost and Tickets - AirTrain - Ground Transportation - John F. Kennedy International Airport - Port Authority of New York & New Jersey |publisher=Panynj.gov |date= |accessdate=2014-05-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524001810/http://www.panynj.gov/airports/jfk-cost-tickets.html |archivedate=2014-05-24 }}</ref>。

